飓风艾瑞丝以风力时速233公里强度从伯利兹登岸，陆地上测得的最高风速是比格克里克一座气象站测得的每小时171公里。风暴的直径较小，因此只给该国南部约110公里范围内的区域造成严重破坏。该区域出现了高达4.6米的[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]{{#tag:ref|[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]指平均潮汐高度和风暴产生潮汐高度之间的差距<ref name="glo" />。|group="注"}}<ref name="tcr" />，浪高则超过4米<ref name="dref1010" />，造成街道洪水泛滥，一些近海珊瑚礁受损<ref name="tour">{{cite report | author = John P. Tiefenbacher | author2 = Carol M. Koenig Stewart | title = The Impacts of Hurricanes Mitch, Keith, and Iris on Tourists, Tourism, and Development in Belize, 1998-2003 | accessdate = 2014-08-02 | year = 2006 | publisher = Applied Geography Conference | url = http://www.academia.edu/172441/THE_IMPACTS_OF_HURRICANES_MITCH_KEITH_AND_IRIS_ON | date =  | archive-date = 2020-04-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200403182729/https://www.academia.edu/172441/THE_IMPACTS_OF_HURRICANES_MITCH_KEITH_AND_IRIS_ON | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

风暴上岸后令数十个村庄的房屋和学校受损<ref name="sitrep5">{{cite report | deadurl = no | title = Caribbean/Belize - Hurricane/Tropical depression Iris OCHA Situation Report No. 5 | date = 2001-10-09 | author = United Nations Office for the Coordination of Humanitarian Affairs | publisher = ReliefWeb | accessdate = 2013-06-23 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714185252/http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/caribbeanbelize-hurricanetropical-depression-iris-ocha-situation-report-no-5 | archivedate = 2014-07-14 | url = http://www.reliefweb.int/report/belize/caribbeanbelize-hurricanetropical-depression-iris-ocha-situation-report-no-5}}</ref>。有35个村庄里超过95%的建筑物被彻底摧毁<ref name="ifrc1012">{{cite report | author = International Federation of Red Cross and Red Crescent Societies | date = 2001-10-12 | title = Belize: Hurricane Iris appeal No. 33/01 | publisher = ReliefWeb | accessdate = 2014-08-02 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/belize-hurricane-iris-appeal-no-3301 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714145039/http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/belize-hurricane-iris-appeal-no-3301 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-07-14}}</ref>。由于气旋的规模较小，因此受灾最严重的主要局限在托莱多区和斯坦克里克区，这两个区位于该国最南部，也是最贫困的区<ref name="dref1010" /><ref name="un1017">{{cite report | author = United Nations | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714155550/http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/united-nations-international-appeal-humanitarian-assistance-and-initial-rehabilitation | date = 2001-10-17 | title = United Nations international appeal for humanitarian assistance and initial rehabilitation activities following Hurricane Iris: launched in Belize on 17 October 2001 | publisher = ReliefWeb | accessdate = 2013-06-28 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/united-nations-international-appeal-humanitarian-assistance-and-initial-rehabilitation | archivedate = 2014-07-14 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。托莱多区有约72%的房屋被毁，斯坦克里克区也有约50%<ref>{{cite report | author = Caribbean Disaster Emergency Response Agency | publisher = ReliefWeb | date = 2001-10-19 | accessdate = 2014-08-02 | title = Hurricane Iris Situation Report #3 | archivedate = 2013-09-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130910114702/http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/hurricane-iris-situation-report-3 | deadurl = no | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/hurricane-iris-situation-report-3}}</ref>，导致约1.5万人流离失所<ref name="ifrc1018">{{cite report | author = International Federation of Red Cross and Red Crescent Societies | date = 2001-10-18 | title = Belize: Hurricane Iris appeal No. 33/01 operations update No. 1 | publisher = ReliefWeb | accessdate = 2014-08-02 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/belize-hurricane-iris-appeal-no-3301-operations-update-no-1 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714163305/http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/belize-hurricane-iris-appeal-no-3301-operations-update-no-1 | archivedate = 2014-07-14}}</ref>。两个区都出现停电，供水也受到污染<ref name="ifrc1012" />。受灾最严重的地区有许多生活在农场的贫困玛雅人失去了绝大部分财产<ref name="ifrc1012" />。接近海岸线的[[珀拉什奇亚|珀拉什奇亚]]（{{lang|en|Placencia}}）有约80%的民房被毁，余下的建筑物中也大部分存在屋顶受损的情况，街上还有许多倒塌的电线杆<ref name="dref1010" />。附近的塞纳拜特（{{lang|en|Seine Bight}}）有约90%的房屋被毁<ref name="ocha1010">{{cite report | author = United Nations Office for the Coordination of Humanitarian Affairs | date = 2001-10-10 | publisher = ReliefWeb | accessdate = 2014-08-02 | title = Caribbean: Belize - Hurricane Iris OCHA Situation Report No. 6 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/caribbean-belize-hurricane-iris-ocha-situation-report-no-6 | archivedate = 2014-07-14 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714161543/http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/caribbean-belize-hurricane-iris-ocha-situation-report-no-6}}</ref>，艾瑞丝登陆的猴河镇则有超过90%的民房毁于一旦<ref name="dref1010" />。伯利兹南部有许多道路和渔业码头受损。飓风还破坏了旅游设施，该国的玛雅遗址也受到轻度影响<ref name="cdera1011">{{cite report | author = Caribbean Disaster Emergency Response Agency | date = 2001-10-11 | title = First Evaluation of Effects of Hurricane Iris | accessdate = 2013-06-25 | publisher = ReliefWeb | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/first-evaluation-effects-hurricane-iris | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714131414/http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/first-evaluation-effects-hurricane-iris | archivedate = 2014-07-14 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，全国有20%的酒店房间受损，损失数额达到3700万美元（2001年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|37000000|2001}}}}美元）<ref name="oas1017">{{cite report | author = Organization of American States | date = 2001-10-17 | title = Belize Ambassador updates OAS on hurricane damage | accessdate = 2014-08-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714152154/http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/belize-ambassador-updates-oas-hurricane-damage | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/belize-ambassador-updates-oas-hurricane-damage | archivedate = 2014-07-14 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。该国其他地区基本上没有受到这场风暴的影响<ref name="rony">{{cite report | author = Rony Maza | date = 2001-10 | title = Reduction of the Impact of Hurricane Iris on the Health of the Affected Population in Belize | publisher = the Pan American Health Organization | accessdate = 2014-08-02 | archivedate = 2014-07-14 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714120843/http://www.docstoc.com/docs/71698355/HURRICANE-IRIS---DOC | deadurl = no | url = http://www.docstoc.com/docs/71698355/HURRICANE-IRIS---DOC}}</ref>。

艾瑞丝产生的狂风对伯利兹南部的农作物构成破坏，有些地方的收割工作才刚刚开始。约有2000公顷香蕉、超过1400公顷水稻和1200公顷玉米被毁，其他农作物的受损程度较轻<ref name="cdera1011" />。风暴还淹没了农田，导致许多牧蓄死亡。由于水受到污染等多种因素的影响<ref name="cdera1011b">{{cite report | author = Caribbean Disaster Emergency Response Agency | date = 2001-10-11 | title = Hurricane Iris Situation Report # 2 | publisher = ReliefWeb | accessdate = 2014-08-02 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/hurricane-iris-situation-report-2 | archive-date = 2021-01-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210121005914/https://reliefweb.int/report/belize/hurricane-iris-situation-report-2 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，[[对虾|对虾]]养殖业的收成减少了四分之一<ref name="cdera1011" />。伯利兹的农作物估计遭受了1.03亿美元（2001年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|103000000|2001}}}}美元）的损失<ref name="oas1017" />，其中香蕉占了大部分<ref name="cdera1011" />。狂风还破坏了大片森林，一些灾区有40%的树木被连根拔起<ref name="cdera1011" />。许多动物的栖息地因此受到影响，猴河附近很可能有大量[[吼猴|吼猴]]死亡<ref name="eprints" />。风暴产生的大浪[[侵蚀作用|侵蚀]]了海滩，但海上所受影响远小于前一年的飓风基斯<ref name="cdera1011" />。不过，风暴过后还是出现了大量鱼类死亡的报道，这可能是由于海水中大量物质腐烂，导致氧含量太低所致<ref name="eprints">{{cite report | author = Jan Meerman | date = 2001-10-05 | title = A first assessment of damage to terrestrial ecosystems in Southern Belize | publisher = Belize Environmental Consultancies Ltd.}}</ref>。

伯利兹全国有3718户民宅受损或被毁<ref name="ifrc123">{{cite report | author = International Federation of Red Cross and Red Crescent Societies | date = 2002-01-23 | title = Belize: Hurricane Iris appeal No. 33/01 operations update No. 3 | publisher = ReliefWeb | accessdate = 2014-08-02 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/belize-hurricane-iris-appeal-no-3301-operations-update-no-3 | archivedate = 2014-07-14 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714195844/http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/belize-hurricane-iris-appeal-no-3301-operations-update-no-3}}</ref>，对2万1568万人直接构成影响<ref name="un1017" />，占该国人口的8.5%<ref name="unicef">{{cite report | author = United Nations Children's Fund | date = 2001-10-25 | title = UNICEF Humanitarian Action: Belize donor update 25 Oct 2001 | publisher = ReliefWeb | accessdate = 2014-08-02 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/unicef-humanitarian-action-belize-donor-update-25-oct-2001 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714145050/http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/unicef-humanitarian-action-belize-donor-update-25-oct-2001 | archivedate = 2014-07-14}}</ref>。有31所学校、17个医疗机构<ref name="un1017" />和21幢政府大楼受损或被毁<ref name="ocha1018">{{cite report | author = United Nations Office for the Coordination of Humanitarian Affairs | date = 2001-10-18 | title = Caribbean: Belize - Hurricane Iris OCHA Situation Report No. 10 and appeal | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714122703/http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/caribbean-belize-hurricane-iris-ocha-situation-report-no-10-and-appeal | archivedate = 2014-07-14 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2013-06-28 | publisher = ReliefWeb | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/caribbean-belize-hurricane-iris-ocha-situation-report-no-10-and-appeal}}</ref>。包括[[高速公路|高速公路]]和桥梁在内的交通基础设施也遭受了约2500万美元（2001年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|25000000|2001}}}}美元）的破坏<ref name="oas1017" />。艾瑞丝一共夺走了伯利兹及其近海共24人的生命<ref name="ifrc1114">{{cite report | author = International Federation of Red Cross and Red Crescent Societies | date = 2001-11-14 | title = Belize: Hurricane Iris appeal No. 33/01 operations update No. 2 | accessdate = 2014-08-02 | publisher = ReliefWeb | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/belize-hurricane-iris-appeal-no-3301-operations-update-no-2 | archivedate = 2014-07-14 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714122714/http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/belize-hurricane-iris-appeal-no-3301-operations-update-no-2}}</ref>，其中包括“舞浪者号”沉船事故的20名遇难者<ref name="arc1012">{{cite report | author = American Red Cross | date = 2001-10-12 | title = Hurricane Iris relief continues | publisher = ReliefWeb | accessdate = 2014-08-02 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/hurricane-iris-relief-continues | archivedate = 2014-07-14 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714184248/http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/hurricane-iris-relief-continues | deadurl = no}}</ref>。该国共计遭受的损失数额约为2.5亿美元（2001年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|250000000|2001}}}}美元）<ref>{{cite report | author = Caribbean Disaster Emergency Response Agency | date = 2001-12-14 | title = Summary of the hurricane season 2001 | publisher = ReliefWeb | accessdate = 2014-08-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714220711/http://reliefweb.int/report/bahamas/summary-hurricane-season-2001 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/bahamas/summary-hurricane-season-2001 | archivedate = 2014-07-14}}</ref>，艾瑞丝由此成为继1961年的[[飓风哈蒂|飓风哈蒂]]以来对该国破坏最严重的风暴<ref name="rony" />。

=== 中美洲其它地区 ===
危地马拉和洪都拉斯因大浪和暴雨引起大范围停电<ref name="afp1009" />。危地马拉的降雨量在76到102毫米之间，引起山洪暴发和山体滑坡，导致近百人受伤<ref name="Guatemala1" />。受灾最重的是该国南部的[[贝登省|贝登省]]<ref>{{cite report | author = Action by Churches Together International | date = 2001-10-18 | title = ACT appeal Guatemala: Emergency relief to hurricane "Iris" victims- LAGU12 | publisher = ReliefWeb | accessdate = 2014-08-02 | archivedate = 2014-07-14 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/guatemala/act-appeal-guatemala-emergency-relief-hurricane-iris-victims-lagu12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714165059/http://reliefweb.int/report/guatemala/act-appeal-guatemala-emergency-relief-hurricane-iris-victims-lagu12 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。全国共有26所学校和2500套民宅受损<ref>{{cite report | date = 2001-10-11 | title = Caribbean: Guatemala/Belize - Hurricane Iris OCHA Situation Report No. 7 | author = United Nations Office for the Coordination of Humanitarian Affairs | accessdate = 2014-08-02 | archivedate = 2014-07-14 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714190814/http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/caribbean-guatemalabelize-hurricane-iris-ocha-situation-report-no-7 | deadurl = no | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/caribbean-guatemalabelize-hurricane-iris-ocha-situation-report-no-7}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | author = Action by Churches Together International | publisher = ReliefWeb | date = 2001-10-09 | accessdate = 2014-08-02 | title = ACT Alert Belize — Guatemala: Hurricane Iris | archivedate = 2014-07-14 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714182929/http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/act-alert-belize-guatemala-hurricane-iris | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/act-alert-belize-guatemala-hurricane-iris}}</ref>。危地马拉全国估计有2.75万人受到这场飓风影响<ref name="Guatemala1">{{cite web | author = Action by Churches Together International | publisher = ReliefWeb | date = 2001-10-18 | accessdate = 2014-08-02 | title = ACT appeal Guatemala: Emergency relief to hurricane "Iris" victims- LAGU12 | archivedate = 2014-07-14 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714165059/http://reliefweb.int/report/guatemala/act-appeal-guatemala-emergency-relief-hurricane-iris-victims-lagu12 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/guatemala/act-appeal-guatemala-emergency-relief-hurricane-iris-victims-lagu12}}</ref>。该国共有8人遇难<ref name="tcr" />，其中两人是因被倒塌的树木砸中后伤重不治<ref name="afp1010">{{cite news | agency = Agence France-Presse | date = 2001-10-10 | publisher = ReliefWeb | accessdate = 2014-08-02 | title = Hurricane Iris left at least 21 dead, thousands of houses damaged | archivedate = 2014-07-14 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714152559/http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/hurricane-iris-left-least-21-dead-thousands-houses-damaged | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/hurricane-iris-left-least-21-dead-thousands-houses-damaged}}</ref>。

风暴残留给墨西哥南部带去暴雨，[[恰帕斯州|恰帕斯州]]的累计降雨量达到122毫米<ref>{{cite report|author=Alberto Hernández Unzón |author2=Cirilo Bravo Lujano |publisher=Servicio Meteorologico Nacional |date=2002-02-28 |title=Huracán Iris |accessdate=2014-08-02 |url=http://smn.cna.gob.mx/ciclones/tempo2001/atlantico/iris/iris.html |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714194212/http://smn.cna.gob.mx/ciclones/tempo2001/atlantico/iris/iris.html |archivedate=2014-07-14 }}</ref>。[[瓦哈卡州|瓦哈卡州]]也出现暴雨，一共导致120套房屋受损。一个村庄爆发[[泥石流|泥石流]]，摧毁了20套房屋，还夺走了一个儿童的生命，该州还有一名男子被洪水卷走后溺亡<ref name="un">{{cite news | title = Oaxaca: 2 muertos por "Iris" | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2011-10-11 | accessdate = 2014-08-02 | archivedate = 2014-07-14 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714201330/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/38494.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/38494.html}}</ref>。

== 善后 ==
10月9日，伯利兹政府发布安全信号，表示风暴已完全过去，重建和损失评估工作拉开帷幕<ref>{{cite web | author = Government of Belize | publisher = ReliefWeb | date = 2001-10-09 | accessdate = 2014-08-02 | title = Belize commences reconstruction efforts after Hurricane Iris | archivedate = 2014-08-02 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140802144601/http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/belize-commences-reconstruction-efforts-after-hurricane-iris-73577202.html | via = PR Newswire | url = http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/belize-commences-reconstruction-efforts-after-hurricane-iris-73577202.html }}</ref>。政府宣布托莱多区和斯坦克里克区成为灾区<ref name="cdera1011b" />，官员还宣布实行[[宵禁|宵禁]]。艾瑞丝过去后次日，伯利兹市的机场得以重新开放，除南部外该国其他所有地区的交通都已恢复正常<ref name="ocha1010" />。南部居民由于无法获取清洁的水源而只能喝下不干净的水<ref name="ifrc1012" />。官员派出多个医疗队前往南部受灾最严重的区域<ref name="dref1010" />。[[贝尔墨邦|贝尔墨邦]]红十字会分会呼吁居民向风暴灾民捐献钱款、衣服和食品<ref name="ocha1010" />。红十字会还开设了多间庇护所，为超过7000人提供食物<ref name="arc1012" />。到了10月19日，伯利兹南部大部分道路都已恢复通行。政府印制了新的邮票帮助支付重建所需，还核定支出120万美元（2001年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|1200000|2001}}}}美元）用于重建受损民宅。为了帮助庄稼受损的农民，伯利兹政府提供了[[化肥|化肥]]和8200公斤玉米种子<ref name="cdera1019" />。风暴过去后，[[世界粮食计划署|世界粮食计划署]]和伯利兹红十字会合作，向约9000户家庭提供食品<ref>{{cite report | author = World Food Programme | date = 2001-10-24 | title = WFP ODM Emergency situation report 24 Oct 2001 | publisher = ReliefWeb | accessdate = 2014-08-02 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/wfp-odm-emergency-situation-report-24-oct-2001 | archivedate = 2014-07-14 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714195855/http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/wfp-odm-emergency-situation-report-24-oct-2001 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。到了10月31日，红十字会已经向受风暴严重影响的4800人提供了毛毯、防水布和卫生用品<ref>{{cite report | author = International Federation of Red Cross and Red Crescent Societies | date = 2001-10-31 | title = Aid distributions to victims of Hurricane Iris in Belize nearing completion | publisher = ReliefWeb | accessdate = 2014-08-02 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/aid-distributions-victims-hurricane-iris-belize-nearing-completion | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714195855/http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/wfp-odm-emergency-situation-report-24-oct-2001 | archivedate = 2014-07-14 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。住房逐渐得到修复，农作物生产到2002年初已恢复正常。2001年[[圣诞节|圣诞节]]前后，伯利兹红十字会向14个受风暴影响村庄的学童提供了礼物<ref name="ifrc123" />。香蕉作物的损失导致2002年的销售下滑了22%，之后情况逐渐有所好转<ref>{{cite report | publisher = United Nations | date = 2004-11 | title = Economic Survey of Latin America and the Caribbean 2003-2004 | page = 286 | format = PDF | url = http://www.eclac.org/publicaciones/xml/8/15398/lcg2255_i.pdf | accessdate = 2016-03-24}}</ref>。

伯利兹政府在艾瑞丝登陆数天后呼吁[[国际社会|国际社会]]提供援助<ref name="wfp1011">{{cite report | author = World Food Programme | date = 2011-10-11 | title = WFP ODM Emergency situation report 11 Oct 2001 | accessdate = 2014-08-02 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/wfp-odm-emergency-situation-report-11-oct-2001 | archivedate = 2014-07-14 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714131727/http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/wfp-odm-emergency-situation-report-11-oct-2001 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，许多国家为此伸出了援手<ref name="ocha1010" />。英国派出一架[[直升机|直升机]]协助损失评估，还有一组人员前去对水源进行净化。美国也派出损失评估组，还捐献了塑料布<ref name="cdera1019" />。危地马拉本已遭受严重损失，但该国政府还是派出一支由来自全国各地成员组成的工作队协助伯利兹的救灾恢复工作<ref>{{cite web | author = Government of Belize | publisher = ReliefWeb | date = 2001-10-18 | accessdate = 2014-08-02 | title = Republic of Guatemala helps | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/belizehurricane-iris-republic-guatemala-helps | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140802152703/http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/belizehurricane-iris-republic-guatemala-helps | archivedate = 2014-08-02 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。墨西哥送来了毛毯、床垫、食品、饮用水和一支医疗队<ref name="cdera1019" />。[[日本|日本]]政府送来了帐篷和毯子<ref>{{cite report | date = 2001-10-15 | title = Emergency aid for Hurricane disaster in Belize | publisher = ReliefWeb | author = Government of Japan | accessdate = 2014-08-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714144704/http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/emergency-aid-hurricane-disaster-belize | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/emergency-aid-hurricane-disaster-belize | archivedate = 2014-07-14 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，[[中华人民共和国政府|中华人民共和国政府]]捐献了230公斤大米和干果<ref name="cdera1019">{{cite report | author = Caribbean Disaster Emergency Response Agency | date = 2001-10-19 | title = Hurricane Iris Relief: Foreign Assistance Matrix 19 Oct 2001 | accessdate = 2013-06-28 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/hurricane-iris-relief-foreign-assistance-matrix-19-oct-2001 | publisher = ReliefWeb | archivedate = 2014-07-14 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714133255/http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/hurricane-iris-relief-foreign-assistance-matrix-19-oct-2001}}</ref>。此外，联合国的多个部门一共捐献了22.5万美元（2001年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|225000|2001}}}}美元）<ref name="ocha1010" />。

风暴过去后，“舞浪者号”沉船事故的美国遇难者遗体被送回弗吉尼亚州里士满<ref name="ap1016" />。为这艘船承保的[[保险公司|保险公司]]与幸存者和遇难者家属达成400万美元（2001年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|4000000|2001}}}}美元）的赔偿协议。“舞浪者号”的运营商在这起事故发生后仍然得以继续经营<ref name="surv" />。

2002年春，[[世界气象组织|世界气象组织]]将本场飓风的名称“艾瑞丝”（{{lang|en|Iris}}）予以退役，今后永远都不会在[[北大西洋热带气旋|北大西洋热带气旋]]命名时采用<ref>{{cite book | author = Jack Beven | author2 = James L. Free | author3 = Gary Padgett | author4 = Sandy Delgado | chapter = B3: What storm names have been retired? | type = FAQ | title = Frequently Asked Questions | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/tcfaqHED.html | chapterurl = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/B3.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140706125924/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/tcfaqHED.html | date = 2011-05-31 | publisher = Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | accessdate = 2014-08-02 | editor = Chris Landsea | editor2 = Neal Dorst | version = 4.5 | archivedate = 2014-07-06 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。用来替换的新名称是“英格丽德”（{{lang|en|Ingrid}}），于[[2007年大西洋飓风季|2007年大西洋飓风季]]期间首度采用<ref name="HURDAT" />，但到了[[2013年大西洋飓风季|2013年大西洋飓风季]]期间再度使用后，由于[[2013年颶風英格瑞|飓风英格丽德]]对墨西哥造成了严重损失，因此这个名称也已退役，由“伊梅尔达”（{{lang|en|Imelda}}）替换<ref>{{cite report | title = WMO retires Ingrid and Manuel for Atlantic and eastern North Pacific basins | date = 2014-04-10 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2014-04-10 | url = http://www.noaanews.noaa.gov/stories2014/20140410_hurricanenameretired.html | archivedate = 2014-04-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140413125823/http://www.noaanews.noaa.gov/stories2014/20140410_hurricanenameretired.html | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

